OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FAs I write this, the working week is
OL,7,Fgetting underway in Iran. The roads
OL,8,Fare busy with cars and taxis, there
OL,9,Fare people walking to the office, a
OL,10,Fman and woman just drove past on a
OL,11,Fmotorbike, her blonde hair catching on
OL,12,Fthe breeze. In the apartment opposite,
OL,13,FI can see a family having breakfast.
OL,15,FIt could be a normal morning in any
OL,16,Fcapital city. A thousand or so miles
OL,17,Faway, however, talks which directly
OL,18,Faffect all these people have just
OL,19,Fbroken down. What that means for them,
OL,20,Fwhat it means for all of us, is not
OL,21,Fyet clear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
