CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FThe Americans are blaming the
OL,7,FIranians, the Iranians are blaming the
OL,8,FAmericans. No surprise there.
OL,10,FMuch will be made of 21 hours of
OL,11,Ftalks, but in reality, it's nothing if
OL,12,Fthere was a real wish to deliver
OL,13,Fchange. It was way too long if both
OL,14,Fsides went determined to hold onto
OL,15,Ftheir positions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
