PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FOver the past six weeks, the United
OL,7,FStates and Israel have thrown almost
OL,8,Feverything militarily at this war.
OL,9,FThey likely will again. But military
OL,10,Fforce has not achieved a single one of
OL,11,Fits myriad objectives.
OL,13,FIn fact, things are far worse as the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz is now crippled with
OL,15,Fthe knock-on global consequences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
