FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FThe fundamental premise that the
OL,7,FIranians would concede as a result of
OL,8,Fthis war has been exposed as a total
OL,9,Fmiscalculation. History, recent and
OL,10,Fancient, teaches how grave that
OL,11,Fmiscalculation was.
OL,13,FThe Iranians did not arrive in
OL,14,FPakistan believing they were beaten or
OL,15,Fweakened. On the contrary, the US
OL,16,Fengaging in talks, spoke to them of
OL,17,Fthe strength of their position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FSo now the choices are even trickier
OL,7,Ffor the United States. Military action
OL,8,Fhasn't achieved its goals, diplomacy
OL,9,Fhasn't either. Will they expand their
OL,10,Fmilitary campaign, probably. Will they
OL,11,Ftry again with diplomacy, maybe.
OL,13,FAre they strategically stuck,
OL,14,Fdefinitely.
OL,16,FAll sides can do more harm to the
OL,17,Fother, and most likely, we will see
OL,18,Fthat. The President's threats to the
OL,19,FIranian delegation, that they were
OL,20,Fonly alive to negotiate, point to his
OL,21,Fthinking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
