OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAt some point, there probably will be
OL,12,Fmore talks, but the damage done
OL,13,Fbetween this moment and that will be
OL,14,Fimmense.
OL,16,FNow it is who can absorb the blows
OL,17,Fbest. History again can teach that
OL,18,FIran is a master.
OL,20,FAlmost forty days of war have not
OL,21,Fsolved this. Forty more will not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
