OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776038571
OL,3,CNo easy outs, as US-Iran talks
OL,4,Ccollapse in Islamabad
OL,6,FAmerican military action might offer a
OL,7,Fperception of leverage, but it has not
OL,8,Fdelivered.
OL,10,FThere was an easy in to this war.
OL,12,FThere are no easy outs.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
